reviewText: Do you know who you sold the copy of a child's wish too. I eager to find someone with a copy of the movie. I will trade or buy i have over 9,000 movies to choose from please let me know

WoW.. This story revolves around a family dealing with the illness of their yongest child.  It also chronicles the family's struggle to survive with the bureaucracy the first Bush administration doled out.. Worth the look.
